        "TextSection": {
            "TextSectionType": "Definition",
            "Contents": "A rare peripheral motor neuropathy characterized by distal slowly progressive muscular weakness childhood-onset amyotrophy and autonomic dysfunction manifesting as profuse sweating cold-induced distal cyanosis orthostatic hypotension and esophageal achalasia. There have been no further descriptions in the literature since 1981."
        },
